	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />BBCode lists are kinda crappy... This works fine:<br /><br /><ul>Random list:<br /><li> First item;</li><li> Second item;</li></ul><br />But when you're replying and quoting individual items in the list you get this:<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">[*] First item;</div><br />...unless you add a new list tag for each quote. Even though that is in fact the expected behavior, it's still annoying, so I just tend to avoid lists.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


